    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still doing this. the lab results came back for the third time today and it's just... nothing. another year of my life gone and i have nothing to show for it. my funding is drying up, my advisor won't even look me in the eye, and i feel like i've just been chasing a ghost for five years. i'm just so incredibly tired. not even the kind of tired sleep fixes, just... tired of existing in this loop. i feel like i've run out of ways to try.",
